table.title: Team Kiwi Racing - Complete Bathurst 1000 results

query: What are the different types of cars used by Team Kiwi Racing during the 2000-2008 period in the Bathurst 1000 races, and in which years were they used?
summary: During the 2000-2008 period, Team Kiwi Racing used a variety of car models in the Bathurst 1000 races. In the years 2000 and 2001, they participated with the Holden VT Commodore. From 2002 to 2003, they switched to the Holden VX Commodore, later using the Holden VY Commodore in 2004, the Holden VZ Commodore in 2005 and 2006, and finally transitioning to the Ford BF Falcon for the 2007 and 2008 races.
